      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When I am in Adam, though I may not sin,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Unto death, a sinner, sentenced I have been;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When in Christ I need not righteously to act,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’m already righteous, justified in fact."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the flesh I need no effort to express"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Marks of Adam’s nature and its sinfulness;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the spirit I need not to strive or strain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I can live as He is and in spirit reign."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thru my death with Christ, from Adam I am free,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thru my life with Christ, new life is given me!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding not the flesh, old Adam cannot move,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit, life divine I prove."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit is God’s saving way,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit, Christ we will display;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit, we can overcome,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit, we the race may run."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit, we the cross will know,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And His resurrection pow’r thru us will flow;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Minding just the spirit, Christ will live thru me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And His life within will reach maturity."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the spirit Christ is life and all to me,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Strengthening and blessing all-inclusively;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Living in the spirit, holiness I prove,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And the triune God within my heart doth move."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    }
  ],
